ğŸš¨ Troubleshooting Common Issues

"Environment Variables Not Loading"

```bash
# Verify .env.local format
cat .env.local
# Should show key=value pairs without spaces around =
```

"QR Code Not Triggering Call"

Â· Check campaign status is "active"
Â· Verify LiveKit service is running
Â· Test with different QR scanner app

"No Audio in Call"

Â· Ensure browser microphone permissions granted
Â· Check Deepgram API key validity
Â· Test with headphones (sometimes speaker issues)

"Lead Not Appearing in Dashboard"

Â· Check Supabase connection
Â· Verify RLS policies aren't blocking inserts
Â· Check browser console for API errors

